This system will be built by visualizations which match to specific neurological tests. These tests will be the base of this system. In the abstract, a test defines a set of measurement fields and how they relate. Then it can generate visualization modules both the raw and normalized fields as needed. A collection of these TestCalculator objects will be combined into a Domain.
